title: Music Club v1.04 - Music, Band, Club, and Party Wordpress Theme
description:
Music Club is the best Wordpress theme for music, club, party, radio station, bands or even entertainment magazine. Music Club comes with great features for music such as floating music player at the bottom of the page. Also has traditional boxed player as well. Music Club has event post type that come with ticket button with 5 tickets status.

Moreover, music album in this theme is genius. When you click on play button on each alum, all song in that album will be fetched to floating player automatically. With the combination of page builder and these great music tools, you will have endless possibilities

Product page: http://themeforest.net/item/music-club-musicbandclubparty-wordpress-theme/7017803

This wordpress theme has been fully nulled, to install simply upload it to your host like you would any other wordpress theme.
